org.eclipse.swt.accessibility

Class AccessibleActionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • SWTEventObject
      • org.eclipse.swt.accessibility.AccessibleActionEvent

  • public class AccessibleActionEvent
extends SWTEventObject
    Instances of this class are sent as a result of accessibility clients sending AccessibleAction messages to an accessible object.
    Since:
    1.4
    See Also:
    AccessibleActionListener, AccessibleActionAdapter
